					<p class="image-description">
						Since it's inception back in 2007, Virgo ArtGallery has endeavoured to help foster and build a lively online arts scene, taking on over 4000 artists, enabling them to sell their artworks across the world. Not only this, we've worked tirelessly to build our range of affordable artworks, to enable more people to enjoy the wonders of art. The Gallery presents curated virtual exhibitions on themes relevant and exciting in the context of contemporary creative culture. Our educational programmes aim to reveal the possibilities of artistic expression to young minds, encourage fresh thought and stimulate innovation.
					</p>		
				</div>
